## Notepad 
- `notepad/`: Working scratch pad for active development thoughts
### Primary Uses:
  - Temporary workspace for brainstorming and planning
  - Communication channel between AI agent and user
  - Documentation of proposed solutions and implementations
### Contents:
  - Feature planning documents
  - Implementation proposals
  - Debugging notes and observations
  - Library/tool evaluations
  - Architecture discussions
  - Temporary documentation
### Workflow:
  - AI writes plans/proposals here for user review
  - User can provide feedback and approvals
  - Content is temporary/disposable
  - Can be cleared/archived as needed
### Format:
  - Simple markdown files
  - Clear file naming for easy reference
  - Informal, working-notes style
  
</rule-extra>